Output demos/shots/_home.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 27
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1180
Set Padding 20
Set Margin 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.3

Hide
Type "UNRAGER_DISABLE_KITTY=1 ./target/release/unrager"
Enter
Sleep 8s
Show

Sleep 2s
Screenshot demos/shots/home.png

Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
